Enum Class Flavor

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<Flavor>
com.example.model.Flavor
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<Flavor>, Constable
public enum Flavor extends Enum<Flavor>
Represents available flavor options for beverages and other menu items. Different flavors may affect the composition and pricing of items.
